@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_anoyux(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.42
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.67) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.96)) * (0.45 - v0))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v2 + 0.56) * (tmp + 0.20 * v1 + 0.87)))
    data[tid] = v0
